    "long_instructions": "## Hardware Troubleshoot Chat\r\n\r\n### Instructions:\r\nYou're an IT Help Desk agent helping Sam troubleshoot their VR headset. Use **deductive reasoning** by asking logical questions to identify the root cause.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### User Profile Card:\r\n- **Name:** Sam R.  \r\n- **Device Type:** Wireless VR Headset  \r\n- **Connected To:** High-performance desktop (CPU + GPU)  \r\n- **Issue Summary:** \"My VR headset keeps losing connection—audio cuts out, the display jitters, and sometimes it goes black mid-game.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Conversation Starters:\r\n- \"Hi Sam! Can you describe what’s happening when you ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Have you checked ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Does the issue happen when you ___ ?\"  \r\n- \"Let’s try ___ and see if that makes a difference!\"  \r\n",
